quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,22,"Dájúdájú ìwọ ti wà nínú ìgbàgbéra níbi èyí. A sì ti ṣí èbìbò (ojú) rẹ kúrò fún ọ báyìí. Nítorí náà, ìríran rẹ yóò ríran kedere ní òní."
  50,23,"(Mọlāika) alábàárìn rẹ̀ yóò sọ pé: “Èyí ti wà nílẹ̀ ni ohun tí ń bẹ ní ọ̀dọ̀ mi (gẹ́gẹ́ bí àkọsílẹ̀ iṣẹ́ rẹ̀).”"
  50,24,"Ẹ̀yin mọlāika méjèèjì,ẹ ju gbogbo aláìgbàgbọ́ olóríkunkun sínú iná Jahanamọ. {1}",1:[Ìyẹn, olùdarí kan àti ẹlẹ́rìí kan nínú àwọn mọlāika.]
  51,16,"Wọn yóò máa gba n̄ǹkan tí Olúwa wọn bá fún wọn. Dájúdájú wọ́n ti jẹ́ olùṣe-rere ṣíwájú ìyẹn."
  51,17,"Wọ́n máa ń sun oorun díẹ̀ nínú òru."
  51,18,"Wọ́n máa ń tọrọ àforíjìn ní àfẹ̀mọ́júmọ́."
  52,7,"Dájúdájú ìyà Olúwa rẹ máa ṣẹlẹ̀."
  52,8,"Kò sí ẹni tí ó máa dènà rẹ̀."
  52,9,"(Ó máa ṣẹlẹ̀) ní ọjọ́ tí sánmọ̀ máa mì tìtì tààrà."
  53,1,"Allāhu fi gbólóhùn kọ̀ọ̀kan nínú al-Ƙur’ān alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé nígbà tí ó bá sọ̀kalẹ̀ láti ojú sánmọ̀ búra.1 {1}",1:[Ìtúmọ̀ kejì ni pé, Allāhu fi ìràwọ̀ nígbà tí ó bá wálẹ̀ (wọ̀ọ̀kùn ní ìdájí) búra. Àmọ́ ìtúmọ̀ àkọ́kọ́ ló súnmọ́ jùlọ ní ìbámu sí sàkánì rẹ̀ pẹ̀lú àwọn āyah tí ó tẹ̀lé e.]
  53,2,"Ẹni yín kò ṣìnà, kò sì sọnù.1 {1}",1:[Ènìyàn “dọlla” nígbà tí ó bá fi àìmọ̀kan sẹ̀sìn. Ènìyàn tí kò tẹ̀lé ìmọ̀ tí ó mọ̀, òun ló “gawā”. Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - kò fi àìmọ̀kan sẹ̀sìn. Kò sì yapa ìmọ̀ tí Allāhu sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún un.]
  53,3,"Àti pé kò níí sọ̀rọ̀ ìfẹ́-inú."